	* gc.c: change full GC timing to keep lower memory usage.

	  Extend heap only at
	  (1) after major GC
	  or
	  (2) after several (two times, at current) minor GC

	  Details in https://bugs.ruby-lang.org/issues/9607#note-9
	  [Bug #9607]

